			<td><br>Bob Greene is executive vice president of advanced services for Starz Entertainment. Greene is responsible for the development of new, broadband and advanced distribution vehicles, including Vongo.  
<BR><BR>
Prior to joining Starz, Greene served as CEO and chairman of Digital Lava Inc., a Los Angeles-based provider of streaming media software and services used by large companies for marketing, sales, corporate communications and financial presentations. 
<BR><BR>
Before Digital Lava, Greene was senior vice president of Lightspan Inc., a San Diego-based developer of interactive educational software. He served for 13 years at Showtime Networks Inc., rising to senior vice president of sales and marketing. </td>
